{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "609c396c-b023-4c10-b017-b500fbbea65d", "type": 201, "content": {"answer_steps": [], "preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/609c396c-b023-4c10-b017-b500fbbea65d@1.pkg/1772597512981/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597513250", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/609c396c-b023-4c10-b017-b500fbbea65d@1.pkg/1772597512981/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597513250"}, "identifier": "609c396c-b023-4c10-b017-b500fbbea65d", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>本题考查公民基本权利的相关知识。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>A：王阿姨参加区人大代表选举属于行使选举权，而非监督权，故A说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>B：赵奶奶领取退休金体现物质帮助权的保障，有助于维护社会公平，故B说法正确。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>C：小林旷课属于未履行受教育义务，但应接受批评教育并改正，而非行政处罚，C说错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>D：李某被强行带走侵犯的是人身自由权，而非隐私权，故B说法错误。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>&nbsp;</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>3.2 依法行使权利</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）八年级（1）班道德与法治老师带领学生在学习&ldquo;理解权利义务&rdquo;这一课后，开展了知识竞赛，下列推导正确的是（ &nbsp; &nbsp; ）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）八年级（1）班道德与法治老师带领学生在学习“理解权利义务”这一课后，开展了知识竞赛，下列推导正确的是（     ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "